      <title>利润率低、维修导致中国 9 月石油进口放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/china-oil-imports-slowed-in-september-on-weak-margins-repairs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于炼油商面临利润率低迷的问题，并关闭工厂进行计划维护，中国上个月石油进口量下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/china-oil-imports-slowed-in-september-on-weak-margins-repairs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 10:09:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求疲软导致中国贷款表现令人失望，但债券提振信贷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/china-s-credit-expansion-tops-forecasts-but-loans-disappoint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管信贷增长超过预期（主要得益于国债销售激增），9月份中国贷款扩张表现令人失望，表明国内需求仍然疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/china-s-credit-expansion-tops-forecasts-but-loans-disappoint</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 09:17:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
